    <summary type="text">Updated to version 1.0.0</summary>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
    <p>Updated to version 1.0.0 of CCSCodeStandard. Changes include:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Enforcing type-based variable name prefixes (e.g., str for String, int for Integer, gc for constants)</li>
    <li>Automatic code fixes to rename variables to the correct prefix</li>
    <li>Detection of missing 'As' clauses in variable declarations</li>
    <li>Code actions to add missing type annotations automatically</li>
    <li>Special handling for fields including public/private distinction and constants</li>
    <li>Support for variable declarations, parameters, and ForEach loop control variables</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This update improves code readability, maintainability, and consistency across your codebase.</p>
]]></content>
